      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. Both its mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation are beyond reproach, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
